<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include("partials/head") %>
  <body>
    <div class="site-shell">
      <%- include("partials/header") %>

      <main>
        <section class="page-hero about-hero">
          <div class="container page-hero-panel">
            <%- include("components/breadcrumbs", { items: [{ label: "About" }] }) %>
            <div class="about-hero-grid">
              <div class="about-hero-copy">
                <span class="eyebrow">About Bilge</span>
                <h1>Bilge Online Institute</h1>
                <p class="about-hero-tagline">Access Wisdom, empower your Future.</p>
                <p>
                  Welcome to Bilge Online Institute, where ambition meets opportunity.
                  In a world being reshaped by technology, economic shifts, and new ways of working,
                  we believe continuous learning is no longer optional. It is essential.
                </p>
                <p>
                  We were founded on a simple but powerful belief: high-quality, career-relevant education
                  should be accessible to everyone, anywhere.
                </p>
                <div class="hero-actions">
                  <a class="button button-cta-light" href="/programmes">Explore programmes</a>
                  <a class="button-secondary" href="/faculty">Meet faculty</a>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="about-hero-aside">
                <div class="about-stat-grid">
                  <article class="about-stat-card">
                    <strong>60+</strong>
                    <span>Professional certificate programmes designed for modern careers.</span>
                  </article>
                  <article class="about-stat-card">
                    <strong>9</strong>
                    <span>Specialized learning domains spanning technology, business, and future skills.</span>
                  </article>
                  <article class="about-stat-card">
                    <strong>Self-paced</strong>
                    <span>Flexible study built for professionals, founders, and lifelong learners.</span>
                  </article>
                  <article class="about-stat-card">
                    <strong>Practitioner-led</strong>
                    <span>Learning shaped by active industry experts, not outdated theory alone.</span>
                  </article>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="section-copy">
              <span class="kicker-label">Who We Are</span>
              <h2>A next-generation digital institute built for the real world.</h2>
              <p>
                Bilge Online Institute is a next-generation digital learning platform offering over 60 professional
                certificate programs across nine specialized domains. From high-demand tech skills like Data Science,
                Cloud Computing, and Blockchain to essential business disciplines such as Project Management and Digital
                Marketing, and future-forward fields like Quantum Computing, IoT, and ESG, our curriculum is built for
                relevance, adaptability, and real career movement.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-story-grid">
              <article class="narrative-card about-story-card">
                <span class="kicker-label">Institution Story</span>
                <h3>We do not just teach theory. We bridge the gap between learning and doing.</h3>
                <p>
                  Bilge is designed for learners who want more than content. We create pathways that connect structured
                  learning, guided practice, and certificate-backed outcomes so learners leave with skills they can use
                  immediately in work, business, and leadership.
                </p>
              </article>

              <article class="feature-panel about-story-card">
                <span class="kicker-label">What Makes Us Different</span>
                <h3>Built around employability, flexibility, and practical capability.</h3>
                <div class="stack-list">
                  <div class="stack-item">
                    <strong>Industry-Aligned Courses</strong>
                    Every certificate is shaped by practitioners so you learn what employers are actually hiring for.
                  </div>
                  <div class="stack-item">
                    <strong>Diverse and Future-Focused</strong>
                    Our catalog spans digital, business, personal growth, language, and specialized industry tracks.
                  </div>
                  <div class="stack-item">
                    <strong>Flexible, Self-Paced Learning</strong>
                    Upskill on your schedule without putting your life or career on hold.
                  </div>
                  <div class="stack-item">
                    <strong>Practical Application</strong>
                    Real-world projects, case studies, and simulations help you graduate with work you can show.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="section-copy section-copy--split">
              <div>
                <span class="kicker-label">Learning Ecosystem</span>
                <h2>Eight pillars that help learners navigate the institute with purpose.</h2>
              </div>
              <p>
                We organize our learning ecosystem into clear pathways so professionals can quickly identify the domain,
                depth, and direction that matches their goals.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-pillars-grid">
              <article class="about-pillar-card">
                <span class="about-pillar-card__number">01</span>
                <h3>Tech &amp; Digital Skills</h3>
                <p>For builders and innovators across data, cloud, DevOps, UX/UI, and applied technology.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="about-pillar-card">
                <span class="about-pillar-card__number">02</span>
                <h3>Business &amp; Management</h3>
                <p>For strategists and leaders pursuing project management, digital marketing, and e-commerce growth.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="about-pillar-card">
                <span class="about-pillar-card__number">03</span>
                <h3>Finance &amp; Professional Services</h3>
                <p>For analysts and wealth creators building strength in modeling, risk, and accounting.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="about-pillar-card">
                <span class="about-pillar-card__number">04</span>
                <h3>Marketing &amp; Communications</h3>
                <p>For storytellers and brand architects in copywriting, podcasting, and social media strategy.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="about-pillar-card">
                <span class="about-pillar-card__number">05</span>
                <h3>Personal &amp; Professional Development</h3>
                <p>For high-performers building public speaking, negotiation, emotional intelligence, and executive presence.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="about-pillar-card">
                <span class="about-pillar-card__number">06</span>
                <h3>Emerging &amp; Future-Focused Domains</h3>
                <p>For pioneers moving into RPA, IoT, quantum computing, and green skills.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="about-pillar-card">
                <span class="about-pillar-card__number">07</span>
                <h3>Language &amp; Communication</h3>
                <p>For global citizens improving business English, Japanese, Korean, Spanish, and cross-border communication.</p>
              </article>
              <article class="about-pillar-card">
                <span class="about-pillar-card__number">08</span>
                <h3>Specialized Industry Tracks</h3>
                <p>For domain experts in healthcare, education, sustainability, and sector-specific excellence.</p>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <div class="container about-promise-grid">
            <article class="quote-card about-quote-card">
              <span class="kicker-label">Our Promise To You</span>
              <blockquote>
                You are not just another enrollment. You are a partner in progress.
              </blockquote>
              <p>
                Whether you are pivoting into Cloud Computing, launching a startup through Entrepreneurship,
                mastering Remote Collaboration, or earning a certificate in Sustainability and Green Skills,
                we are here to guide, train, and equip you.
              </p>
              <p>
                The future does not wait for the perfect resume. It rewards the curious, the persistent, and the skilled.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="narrative-card about-checklist-card">
              <span class="kicker-label">What This Means For You</span>
              <h3>Learning that stays current, practical, and deeply connected to real work.</h3>
              <div class="about-checklist">
                <div class="about-check-item">No outdated slides from 2019.</div>
                <div class="about-check-item">No textbook-only theory.</div>
                <div class="about-check-item">No "do as I say, not as I do" teaching culture.</div>
                <div class="about-check-item">Confidence built through practitioner-led learning and real application.</div>
              </div>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="section-copy">
              <span class="kicker-label">Instructor Promise</span>
              <h2>Not just credentialed. Competent.</h2>
              <p>
                At Bilge Online Institute, we know a curriculum is only as good as the person teaching it.
                That is why we made a core promise: every instructor is a practitioner first.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-instructor-grid">
              <article class="feature-panel about-instructor-panel">
                <h3>Learn from active professionals who care.</h3>
                <p>
                  Our instructors do not just lecture. They mentor. They host live Q&amp;A sessions,
                  review real submissions, and share the thinking behind the work so learners understand both
                  the "how" and the "why."
                </p>
                <div class="stack-list">
                  <div class="stack-item">
                    <strong>Active Industry Professionals</strong>
                    Teaching is grounded in current market practice and professional responsibility.
                  </div>
                  <div class="stack-item">
                    <strong>Practitioners Who Care</strong>
                    Learners benefit from shortcuts, mistakes, lessons, and frameworks built in the field.
                  </div>
                  <div class="stack-item">
                    <strong>Always Current</strong>
                    Course materials are reviewed and refreshed quarterly as technology and markets evolve.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>

              <article class="narrative-card about-assessment-card">
                <span class="kicker-label">5-Pillar Competency Assessment</span>
                <h3>Every instructor is rigorously vetted before stepping into the classroom.</h3>
                <div class="about-assessment-list">
                  <div class="about-assessment-item">
                    <span class="about-assessment-item__index">1</span>
                    <div>
                      <strong>Real-world experience</strong>
                      Minimum 5+ years in their professional domain.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-assessment-item">
                    <span class="about-assessment-item__index">2</span>
                    <div>
                      <strong>Teaching excellence</strong>
                      Proven ability to explain complex ideas simply and clearly.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-assessment-item">
                    <span class="about-assessment-item__index">3</span>
                    <div>
                      <strong>Current certifications</strong>
                      Relevant certifications such as AWS, PMP, Google Cloud, and other domain credentials where applicable.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-assessment-item">
                    <span class="about-assessment-item__index">4</span>
                    <div>
                      <strong>Portfolio of results</strong>
                      Evidence of campaigns, code, systems, case studies, or designs they have led.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-assessment-item">
                    <span class="about-assessment-item__index">5</span>
                    <div>
                      <strong>Peer feedback</strong>
                      A continuous rating and review system that keeps teaching quality accountable.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
          <div class="container cta-panel about-cta-panel">
            <span class="eyebrow">Join Bilge</span>
            <h3>Build your future with a global community of lifelong learners.</h3>
            <p>
              Start today at Bilge Online Institute and learn from the best in the business.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
              <a class="button button-cta-light" href="/programmes">Start with programmes</a>
              <a class="button-secondary" href="/admissions">Admissions</a>
              <a class="button-ghost" href="/contact">Contact us</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>

      <%- include("partials/footer") %>
    </div>
    <script src="/public/js/website-theme.js" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
